rooms.Name: The gates to the Newbie Forest
rooms.Description:
You've arrived at the entrance to the Newbie Forest.  There's a
forest ranger here warning tourists and campers about the safety
hazards while visiting the forest grounds.  The ranger is also
checking to see if you have the qualifications to enter this
forest-land because of the level restrictions to enter this
area.  You can see the grand forest from outside the gates.  The
lush, green plants and trees from the distance is just splendid
and the smell of fresh pine is everywhere.  There are animals
there running and pouncing happily as though they have nothing to
fear.  This beautiful forest lights up as the sun begins to rise
from a distance.

rooms.Name: Welcome to the Newbie Forest!
rooms.Description:
You have arrived at the entrance of the Newbie Forest where
animals here roam free in the wild.  Everywhere you look, there
are various kinds of plants and trees covering the forest
grounds.  The howls of animal cries and the chirping of birds are
all parts of what make this forest so lively and beautiful.  
There are no paths to take here because the Newbie Forest has an
enviroment that's intolerant to even the slightest changes by
deforestation.  The forest here is not vast nor is it borderless.
It's merely a place where the newbie-kinds "participate" in the
population control of animals which would help to stabilize the
forest's enviroment.  The Newbie Forest continues north.

rooms.Name: Southeastern part of Newbie Forest
rooms.Description:
Trees and shrubberies are lying all over the forest grounds.  The
scenic path you're taking is more like an obstacle.  You are
constantly leaping over thorny bushes and small puddles of muddy
water.  The gentle animals here are abundant and they pass you by
as though you are of no threat to them.

rooms.Name: Northwestern part of Newbie Forest
rooms.Description:
As you walk along this section of the forest, you notice a narrow
fresh-water stream to your north.  The water is sparkling fresh
and you can see the pink salmons swimming upstream to spawn.  The
small stream seems to lead southeast of here, maybe all the way
to the waterfall.

rooms.Name: Far Northern part of Newbie Forest
rooms.Description:
It's strange that when you enter deeper into this forest the
sunlight seems to get dimmer and dimmer.  Maybe it's the tall,
ancient trees that provide an enormous canopy.  As you walk
further north of here, you would notice a murky swamp just ahead
of you...it doesn't look safe in there...

rooms.Name: Far Northern part of Newbie Forest
rooms.Description:
Trees and shrubberies are lying all over the forest grounds.  The
scenic path you're taking is more like an obstacle.  You are
constantly leaping over thorny bushes and small puddles of muddy
water.  The gentle animals here are abundant and they pass you by
as though you are of no threat to them.

rooms.Name: The Swamp
rooms.Description:
The dirty, mosquito-infested swamp water covers you from the
waist down.  You've entered into the area of the forest where
it's not safe nor is it beautiful.  As you walk through this 
thick and mucky water, you sense something is staring right at
you.  There's also something moving in the water...something that
looks big, and it's headed to your direction!

rooms.Name: The Swamp
rooms.Description:
You are becoming nauseated by the putrid smell of the swamp
water.  As you try making your way through this obstacle, you
can feel the mosquitoes biting at your exposed skin and the
bloodsucking leeches trying to make a supper on your legs.

rooms.Name: The Swamp
rooms.Description:
This section of the Newbie Forest is indeed dangerous...  You can
see the hungry alligators here swimming closer and closer to you.
There are large anacondas dangling on the trees waiting to spring
on an unsuspecting victim.  Everywhere you look, all the 
creatures here look threatening unlike the other beasts in the
Newbie Forest.

rooms.Name: The Swamp
rooms.Description:
You are getting tired and desparate to get back to land.  The
alligators are still stalking you...they're coming closer and
closer...  The staring eyes of predatory beasts surround you 
everywhere you go.  As you move through this thick swamp water,
you sense that land is nowhere close to your location.

rooms.Name: Far Northern part of Newbie Forest
rooms.Description:
Trees and shrubberies are lying all over the forest grounds.  The
scenic path you're taking is more like an obstacle.  You are
constantly leaping over thorny bushes and small puddles of muddy
water.  The gentle animals here are abundant and they pass you by
as though you are of no threat to them.

rooms.Description:

scenic path you're taking is more like an obstacle.  You are
constantly leaping over thorny bushes and small puddles of muddy
water.  The gentle animals here are abundant and they pass you by
as though you are of no threat to them.

rooms.Name: Far Northern part of Newbie Forest
rooms.Description:
As you struggle to make your way around this forest, you come
across a very narrow path.  You wonder to yourself, who could
live inside this wild forest area?  The path looks like it will
take you further north of here.

rooms.Name: Along a narrow path
rooms.Description:
This road is in fact, man-made.  You can see the marble stones
lying on both sides of the road as though they were put there for
a decorative purpose.  This narrow path seems to lead to that
small cabin just north of here.  The cabin from a distance looks
new, and you can see the smoke coming out of its chimney.

rooms.Name: Hunter Bob's Cabin
rooms.Description:
This place is absolutely fit for a king to live in.  You feel the
warmth of the burning logs in the fireplace as soon as you step
into this small cabin.  There's a large bearskin rug on the floor
and the animal-head trophies are stapled to the walls.  Stuffed
animals are left everywhere as a decoration to this crowded room 
and prized hunter rifles are displayed on wooden racks.  In the
center of the room, you see a man dressed in a hunter's vest
cleaning a long rifle.  He looks like he's about to get ready to
do some hunting.

rooms.Name: Along a narrow path
rooms.Description:
The narrow path is becoming broader and broader.  You finally
arrived at your destination!  The walnut-oak door is north of
you and it looks unlocked.  Everywhere you look, you sense that
the person who built this grand cabin must be a skilled carpenter.

rooms.Name: A narrow stream
rooms.Description:
Though this stream looks narrow, it still has a powerful current.
You feel the force of the stream is pushing you southeast of
here.  The fresh-water fishes pass you by very quickly as they
struggle to fight the current and make it upstream.

rooms.Name: Along a narrow stream
rooms.Description:
The powerful stream current has forced you to move southeast
of here.  The water is now looking deeper...the stream is 
becoming more like a wild river.  You're struggling to keep
yourself under control and not to be swept right onto a hard
rock.  The powerful stream continues southeast of here.

rooms.Name: Along a narrow stream
rooms.Description:
The powerful currents seem to be dying slowly...  There must be
something up ahead that is blocking the narrow stream.  You don't
feel anything pushing against you nor resticting your movement.
The stream continues southeast.

rooms.Name: Along a narrow stream
rooms.Description:
This stream seems to be continuous.  You're beginning to get sea-
sick from the swaying and rocking.  Suddenly, you spot something
southeast of here...it looks like some sort of a beaver dam is
built there.

rooms.Name: A beaver dam
rooms.Description:
You are amazed by this dam structure.  It doesn't look like
anything a beaver could built.  The structural plans of this
large dam looked more like the work of a man rather than a beast.
The stones and wood used to build this dam is stacked nicely
together which makes you suspicious that this is the work only an
intelligent being could do.  The dam is about ten feet tall and
is quite thick.  There seems to be no way of getting pass
it...hmmm, wait a sec, there's a path that'll take you out of the
stream and out of the bank.  The path is east of here.

rooms.Name: A narrow, rocky path
rooms.Description:
This path is much more narrow than the stream you came from.
There are rocks that seem to be laid evenly on the road as though
someone arranged them that way.  Ouch!  The small rocks are 
hurting your poor feet...  The path continues east of here.

rooms.Name: A narrow, rocky path
rooms.Description:
Your feet are bloodied by the small, hard rocks that you have
stepped on.  You cursed at the prankster responsible for laying
out all these rocks on the path.  But what reason would anyone do
such a trick...unless of course, that person was trying to stop 
you from reaching a certain place...  The path continues east.

rooms.Name: End of the narrow, rocky path
rooms.Description:
*Whew*  Finally, you can rest those poor feet of yours.  The path
stops here and there's no more small rocks on the ground that'll
hurt you.  As you rest yourself, something from a distance 
catches your eye.  It's a strange patch of mushrooms that's
bunched up together to look like a city.  The mushrooms are
unusually large and...what's this...there seems to be little blue
bugs moving around in that mushroom patch...hmmm, curious...
The path to the mushroom patch is south of here.

rooms.Name: A very, VERY narrow path
rooms.Description:
Egads, whoever made this path must be a dwarf.  The clearing for
this road is a bit too narrow for any man to move around.  You
are headed towards the mushroom patch and as you begin moving
closer to the patch, you can see a beggar and a cat there
stomping on some blue bugs.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
The little blue creatures are scattering everywhere.  The wide
spread panic is forcing them to secure themselves in their
mushroom houses.  As you walk through this mushroom village you
would notice that some of these creatures are throwing rocks at
you to prevent you from going any further into the village.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
As you entered this mushroom patch, you are astonish to find out
that those "blue bugs" are actually small intelligent creatures.
These little creatures seem to inhabit those funny-looking 
mushrooms.  All the blue creatures look fearful from some
disturbance in their village...maybe, it's because that old,
disgusting beggar and his mangy cat are trying to catch them.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
You can hear the creatures yell out, 'Run for your lives!'  As
you walk further through the village, the creatures begin
throwing weightless pebbles at you.  You are fascinated by how
these creatures are trying to stop you from advancing towards 
the center of the village.  The small, harmless rocks that they
throw at you barely even sting you.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
As you slowly and carefully walk inside this strange village.
You notice a strange-looking mushroom house east of here.
There's a windmill outside of it.  There door looks too small for
you to open and go in...so why not just open up the roof and see
what's inside...

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
You feel powerful as you walk inside this small village.  There's
nothing here that can hurt you, not even those intelligent little
creatures.  As you walk along this village, you notice a small
blue creature tripping and falling on his face before making his
way inside a mushroom house.  His house is west of where you're
standing and it looks way too small for you to make an entrance
through the door.

rooms.Name: Clumsy Smurf's House
rooms.Description:
You ripped open the roof and quickly looked around this place
with curiosity.  There's really nothing special about this
place...it looks like your pad back home, only that it's much
smaller.  A clumsy-looking creature is here tripping and falling
from panic.  He wasn't expecting any company today.

rooms.Name: Handy Smurf's Workshop
rooms.Description:
As soon as you opened up the roof and put your big, fat foot
inside this little mushroom, a blue creature living inside
screams out in fear.  This strange-looking mushroom house is
filled with gadgetries and machines.  Everywhere you look, tools
are spread out on the floor and on the tables.  The frighten
little smurf that lives in here don't seem to be too frighten
anymore.  In fact, he's pulling out a strange gadget from his
toolbox and pointing that thing right at you!

rooms.Name: Hefty's Gym
rooms.Description:
Crack!  You open the roof and quickly stare at the brave creature
as though you're about to pound him to smithereens.  But the
creature here looks undaunted by you.  He stands with his chest
thrusted and fists closed.  As you begin to laugh at this silly
little creature, you looked around his house.  It seems to
resemble more like a gyn than a place you would live in.  There
are weights and dumbells all over the floor.  You see wooden
benches and assort weightlifting equipments all over the place,
from wall to wall.  This little creature must be the local   
strong man in the village.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
Your thunderous stomps are creating an earthquake for these little
creatures.  You see them lose their footing and fall to their
face.  The sounds of your wicked laugh is beginning to bring fear
to the poor helpless creatures.  As you move along through the
village, you see one of the creatures standing in your way.  He
kicked you on the left foot and boy, did that give you a sting.
The little pugnacious creature quickly ran inside his house since
he figger he may not be your match, and slam the door.  His
little mushroom house is to the east of you.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
Wide spread panic is everywhere...  Everyone of these little
creatures are running for cover!  As you walk through this
section of the village, one of the small little creatures threw a
minature banana cream pie right at your face!  He quickly ran to
his mushroom house...laughing out loud!

rooms.Name: Jokey Smurf's Funhouse
rooms.Description:
The little prankster jumps in fear as you open the rooftop.  The
creature gives you a smile and asks you if you like his little
joke.  As you reach inside to grab him you notice his little
shop is filled with gift-wrapped presents.  Hmmm, maybe you might
want to open one up to see what's inside...oh well, maybe later.
The little creature must be a local giftshop owner or something 
like that.

rooms.Name: Vanity's Powder Room
rooms.Description:
You opened the roof as quickly as possible to see what's inside.
This place is totally immaculate.  The bed is made and the floor  
looks spotless and the furniture is also dust-free.  There are 
mirrors everywhere you look.  The walls are just full of nothing
but mirrors...

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
The creatures living in this village is becoming more and more
tense.  They are throwing more rocks at you and also at the
disgusting-looking beggar and his cat.  The beggar seems to be
laughing as though he's mad. 
As you walk along this village, you notice an extremely clean
mushroom house west of here.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
The little mushroom village continues north of here and all the
tiny creatures seem to be headed to that direction.  Someone of
great importance may be living down that way.  Maybe it's the
creature's leader.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
You easily made your way across to the other end of the village.
The creatures are still running back and forth as though they
don't know where to go or what to do.  Everyone of them is
screaming for someone...someone named "Papa Smurf."
There's an odd-looking blue creature running towards a mushroom
house to the east.  He's wearing some goofy spectacles.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
You are coming closer to the end of the village.  There are more
village areas to the southwest of here.  All of these creatures
seem to be pushing their way towards that direction.  Everyone of
them are yelling for help from a certain creature named "Papa Smurf."

rooms.Name: Farmer Smurf's vegetable patch
rooms.Description:
As you walk on the patch, you notice one of the small creature is
yelling at you to get off his field.  He's planting something
here on this small plot of land and it seems you just ruin a
season's worth of crop.  The little creature is dressed in an
overall and a plaid shirt.  He's wearing a straw hat and wielding
a hoe.  This creature must be some sort of a farmer for the village.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
You are coming closer to the end of the village.  The little
creatures are still running in fear and are throwing more little
rocks at you.  There's a small vegetable patch to the east of
here and the rest of the village continues west of here.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
Boom!  Boom!  Boom!  Your loud footsteps are rocking the village.
Houses are collapsing because of your every movement.  The little
creatures here are running back and forth, crying for help.  Your
little visit here on the village is worst than if an earthquake
would to hit this city.

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
The mushroom village is coming to an end.  As you walk along this
section of the village, you notice more mushroom houses south of
here.  Those houses seem to be hidden from the rest, maybe the
leader of these creatures lives in one of those mushrooms.

rooms.Name: Smurfette's Dreamhouse
rooms.Description:
This used to be a great dreamhouse but now it has been crushed by
the earthquake that you've created with your devastating footsteps.
You peek inside this pink mushroom house to see what's inside.
The pace is almost entirely pink.  The walls are pink, the floor is
pink, the furnitures are pink...etc.  There's a strange-looking
creature living here.  Unlike the other creatures, this one has long
blonde hair and it's wearing a white skirt-dress.  It's also 
carrying a tiny blue baby!

rooms.Name: The Smurf Village
rooms.Description:
All of the strange blue creatures seem to be headed here.  The
leader of these critters must live in one of the two houses here.
One of the houses already has a roof collapse on it but the
other seems to be stronger and stays intact.  There seems to be
some sort of magic aura that surrounds that mushroom house to
your east...

rooms.Name: Papa Smurf's Laboratory
rooms.Description:
You ripped open the roof and inside you see a lot of tubes and
beakers everywhere.  This must be a laboratory of some sort and
the creature that lives here is still experimenting with various
kinds of liquids.  This creature living here looks wise and much
older than the rest of the others.  He has a white beard and he
wears a red spandex pants and a red cap.  The creature seems to
be planning on something...maybe he's trying to make a powerful
potion that would force all the invaders out of this once-quiet
and peaceful village.

rooms.Name: Brainy's Library
rooms.Description:
All of the books that used to be on the shelf is now lying all
over the floor.  A nerdy-looking creature is here quickly trying
to pick up the books and reshelf them.  This place is filled with
a variety of different books on all kinds of subjects.  It's like
a library in here.  The nerdy creature must be some sort of a 
librarian or a book collector.
